reformulateUpdatingMenus	"Give any updating menu morphs in the receiver a fresh kiss of life"	(self submorphs		select: [:m | m isKindOf: UpdatingMenuMorph])		do: [:m | m updateMenu			"NB: to do the perfect job here one might well want to extend			across allMorphs here, but the expense upon project entry is			seemingly too high a price to pay at this point"]